{"tid":123930,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[真人化] JOJO第四部不滅鑽石 公佈另外四位角色造型","createTime":"2017-02-17T07:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T15:51:10.000Z","uid":31174,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"70e7678abe64856697b242fc729eb32c97355675","tid":123930,"uid":31174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T07:58:54.000Z","msg":"明明連登咁多JOJO fans<br />\n但係又好似冇乜人提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以就等我開個post黎講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M63hQad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM63hQad.jpg&h=c4ae44d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然個人對JOJO真人化呢件事幾反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過作為JOJO fans都會留意下呢套野嘅發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n繼之前公佈左嘅東方仗助，今次公佈埋另外四位主要角色。<br />\n<br />\n首先係唔係矮仔嘅康一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eRcZ069.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeRcZ069.jpg&h=5e919fc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再跟住係由花子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n216475.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn216475.jpg&h=dceb1f61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n形兆同億泰兩兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/132d37d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F132d37d.jpg&h=5cfee7bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OnqE7Ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOnqE7Ea.jpg&h=ac1d262b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲差我承太郎同埋片桐安十郎仲未公佈<br />\n而家都唔抱有太大期望...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係希望承太郎唔好搞到咁柒<br />\n最關心都係啲替身同埋ORAORA DORARARA 係會俾佢地玩成點..."},{"pid":"626ad911f38ec035bd8f2f8e6e687ef49ffa7226","tid":123930,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T08:01:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">明明連登咁多JOJO fans<br />\n但係又好似冇乜人提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n所以就等我開個post黎講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n有乜好提, 根本係黑歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c90f202452160addf9bb085720a1343c4bbed9","tid":123930,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T08:03:08.000Z","msg":"等第五部動畫算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb392254a1c4278bafcf489282ff9382ed45010","tid":123930,"uid":33721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T08:05:47.000Z","msg":"唔知想點"},{"pid":"13c16e69661dc49ff37e45e57b2e5677b490445c","tid":123930,"uid":33491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T08:34:19.000Z","msg":"又係神木隆之介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd1e128c28b00989e1c44cacb52cadb6803c5b3f","tid":123930,"uid":61269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T09:09:38.000Z","msg":"咁吉良吉影呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw真人版好7"},{"pid":"f0c375e2f6c7abb97e5716071470a294437251be","tid":123930,"uid":34665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T09:20:19.000Z","msg":"做壞哂套漫畫"},{"pid":"09c1d9ffc